00:03:16.815 --> 00:03:18.135
Formulas and tricks.

00:03:18.434 --> 00:03:20.174
So how do you master this?

00:03:20.415 --> 00:03:24.434
First for dates, always note the
issue, date, and the effective date.

00:03:24.795 --> 00:03:28.095
For limits and rates, you have
to memorize key numbers, like

00:03:28.095 --> 00:03:30.285
transaction limits or capital ratios.

00:03:30.464 --> 00:03:31.214
It's non-negotiable.

00:03:32.080 --> 00:03:36.550
Next, identify keywords or
unique phrases linked to specific

00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:38.590
circulars like ombudsman scheme.

00:03:38.980 --> 00:03:42.580
Always understand the purpose, the
core reason behind the circular.

00:03:42.880 --> 00:03:48.460
And please get familiar with all the
acronyms like L-T-V-C-A-R, and KYC.

00:03:48.850 --> 00:03:53.230
A great memorization tip is to group
circulars by theme, like putting

00:03:53.230 --> 00:03:56.890
all digital payment circulars
together to build mental connections.

00:03:57.130 --> 00:03:58.960
Flashcards are your best friend here.

